description: Meghan Markle's new Lemonada podcast has plummeted out of the Spotify 100 list, both in the US and UK. Her latest episode also failed to crack Apple's Top 200 chart.
title: Meghan Markle's podcast Confessions of a Female Founder proves a chart flop - and is beaten by show about sleep

description: The cholesterol-lowering drug has been dished out to an extra 175,000 patients in the last six months alone after the NHS increased testing for those at risk of deadly heart conditions.
title: Unhealthy lifestyles and high cholesterol trigger boom in statin prescriptions to record 3.8 million
